metadata.name: Western Motel
metadata.description:
It was a beautiful day in the state of Oklahoma. I had been driving countless hours through Route 66 as I was making my way to New York. No responsibilities to worry about for a few days, windows down while blasting to music and taking as many photographs as I could. It was a really fun road trip that I would never forget.

Artist: JennVisuals

Limited Edition of 10.
